Battera::

She wasn't sure about rejoining any group. So far, all the groups she 
had been with had betrayed her.  She lowered her head,"I...I don't 
know. I'm not sure if that is the best thing to do. WHy do you want 
me to go with you?"  She sighed heavily. "I'll go back with you. But 
you must promise me that if one of my," she wasn't sure if she should 
finish the sentance or not,"my old leaders is there, that you'll let 
me leave."
